28:48.894 --> 28:50.520
<i>being gracious to anybody or</i>

28:50.521 --> 28:53.356
<i>Adam Sandler making a good movie.</i>

28:53.357 --> 28:56.484
<i>Basically, a magical unicorn is
going to land in front of me</i>

28:56.485 --> 29:00.029
<i>and shower me with candy and
Vicodins before I shoot a</i>

29:00.030 --> 29:02.824
<i>freaking turkey on camera.</i>

29:04.577 --> 29:07.328
<i>That shot you heard was me
shooting a producer in the calf</i>

29:07.329 --> 29:09.205
<i>and telling him to wobble over to the Piggy Wiggly</i>

29:09.206 --> 29:13.001
<i>for a frozen gobbler before he bleeds out.</i>

29:16.755 --> 29:19.131
<i>And like magic, behold.</i>

29:19.132 --> 29:20.800
<i>Turkey.</i>

29:21.885 --> 29:24.220
<i>Slow, slow barbecued turkey,</i>

29:24.221 --> 29:28.641
<i>with all the sides you want and need.</i>

29:28.642 --> 29:30.560
What do we got going on here?

29:30.561 --> 29:32.228
Pigs feet and collard greens.

29:32.229 --> 29:33.688
Pickled pigs feet and collard greens.

29:33.689 --> 29:35.189
Oh, yes.

29:35.190 --> 29:37.525
Barbecue coleslaw.

29:37.526 --> 29:39.694
Potato salad and ramps.

29:39.695 --> 29:41.987
Baked red peas.

29:41.988 --> 29:44.073
There's my weakness right there.

29:44.074 --> 29:45.950
We made you some very special...

29:45.951 --> 29:47.159
Mac and cheese.

29:47.160 --> 29:49.036
Bright orange mac and cheese.

29:49.037 --> 29:51.122
I do like bright orange mac and cheese as you know.

29:51.123 --> 29:52.290
That's a turkey.

29:52.291 --> 29:53.625
Yep.

29:53.626 --> 29:55.543
Let that to be lesson to you.

29:55.544 --> 29:57.836
Like going to Grandma's house.

