<i>and Jeff Allen, owner of Rebellion Farm.</i>

30:02.760 --> 30:06.596
Are there like you guys others -

30:06.597 --> 30:09.181
basically keeping it real as far

30:09.182 --> 30:11.100
as real Southern culinary traditions

30:11.101 --> 30:13.645
as opposed to the jokey ones?

30:13.646 --> 30:15.813
More than you think.

30:15.814 --> 30:18.023
How many people is that?

30:18.024 --> 30:20.526
12.

30:20.527 --> 30:22.903
Yeah, in a town like this, that's pretty amazing.

30:22.904 --> 30:24.656
Goddamn, this is good.

30:24.657 --> 30:27.158
Pigs feet and green, this is ridiculously good.

